import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'


function HotelDetail() {
  return (
    <HotelDetailContainer>
      <HotelImage src={'http://www.jjtravelonline.com/images/inner-services/hotel-inner.png'} />
      <HotelInfo>
        <Availability>Entire Apartment</Availability>
        <Title>South Central</Title>
        <Popularity></Popularity>
        <RoomsDescription></RoomsDescription>
        <Address></Address>
        <Price></Price>
        <Rating></Rating>
      </HotelInfo>
    </HotelDetailContainer>
  )
}

export default HotelDetail

const HotelDetailContainer = styled.div`
display:flex;
width : 80%;
height : 180px;
`
const Availability = styled.p``
const Title = styled.h3``
const Popularity = styled.div``
const RoomsDescription = styled.p``
const Address = styled.p``
const Price = styled.p``
const Rating = styled.p``
const HotelImage = styled.img`
width:40%;
`
const HotelInfo = styled.div`
width: 60%;
`
